snippet.title: The LONGER YOU WATCH, the FUNNIER IT GETS! - Funny DOG VIDEOS
snippet.description:
The hardest try not to laugh challenge ever! Dogs and puppies are so super funny, they just never fail to make us laugh! Really great and hilarious animals! Look how all these dogs and puppies, fail, make funny sounds, play, sleep,... So super funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
